eigenvalues3 <- pca_data3$sdev^2

In [153]:
weights3.2 <- eigenvectors3[, 1:4]

    weights3.2[i, ] <- weights3.2[i, ] * eigenvalues3[i]

    as.data.frame() %>%
    transmute(weight = PC1 + PC2 + PC3 + PC4)
